      • validate

        void validate(UUID sessionId)
        Validates the contents of the specified session asynchronously and sends an EditorSessionValidationCompleteNotificationMessage when the validation is complete. The latest validation results can be retrieved by calling getValidationResults(UUID).
        Parameters:
        sessionId - the session ID

      • validateSync

        void validateSync(UUID sessionId)
        Validates the contents of the specified session, i.e. waits for the validation to complete before returning. Does not send a notification message. The latest validation results can be retrieved by calling getValidationResults(UUID).
        Parameters:
        sessionId - the session ID
